entries.femaleVariant: D'ya know why they had to make him CEO?
'Cause buyin' 'im from Militech was so expensive – now they're embarrassed…
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="飲み過ぎよ、チューマ… 本当はそんなこと思ってないでしょ…" t="C'mon, choom, you're wasted – you don't really think that..." b="" a=""/>
Lemme tell you somethin' – there ain't nothin' worse than a gonk boss.
Oh man, you gonna regret sayin' this tomorrow morning.
I don't regret shit. If he was here, I'd tell him to his fuckin' face!
<kiroshi l="jpn" o="ええ、これで十分。有意義な夜だったわね" t="Yeah, we can go. This was a very productive evening." b="" a=""/>
